<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM8.5.4">
<l>kayaṅkoḷ puṇtalaik kaḷiṟuntu ventiṟal kaḻalmaṉṉar perumpōril</l>
<l>mayaṅka veṇcaṅkam vāyvait tamaintaṉum vantilaṉ maṟikaṭalnīr</l>
<l>tayaṅku veṇtirait tivalainuṇ paṉiyeṉun taḻalmukan tiḷamulaimēl</l>
<l>iyaṅku mārutam vilaṅkile ṉāviyai yeṉakkeṉap peṟalāmē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>That man who in the great war placed at his lips the white conch to confound</l>
<l>Cruel, courageous kings with battle anklets who drive elephants</l>
<l rend="indent">whose heads have deep wounds, he does not come [here].</l>
<l>The wind which, having gathered up embers,</l>
<l rend="indent">[otherwise] called droplets of fine mist from white waves</l>
<l rend="indent">which crash in the roiling seawater,</l>
<l>Rushes against my young breasts, [only] if it stops,</l>
<l rend="indent">may I get to call my life mine.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
